ue\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531306\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531306\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qkw1665702654897.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qkw1665702654897.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qkw1665702654897.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qkw1665702654897\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Working with DTDs\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19628e1_d19629e1_d19630e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open or create a DTD:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19631e1_d19632e1_d19633e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the Uniface IDE, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More Editors &gt;DTD</span></span>.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19634e1_d19635e1_d19636e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__p_d38855e1_d38856e1_d38857e1\">Select an existing DTD or enter the name of\n                     a new DTD. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">The Define DTD dialog box is displayed. This is the main interface of the\n                     DTD Editor.</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19637e1_d19638e1_d19639e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To open a DTD from a file:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19640e1_d19641e1_d19642e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the DTD Editor, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Load from file...</span></span> and open the desired DTD file.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19643e1_d19644e1_d19645e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Save</span></span> or compile the DTD to store the DTD in the Repository.\n </span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19646e1_d19647e1_d19648e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To define a DTD, you can generate a DTD from modeled entities or component data structures, or you can manually define a DTD. For more information, see:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19652e1_d19653e1_d19654e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pkq1665702655042.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pkq1665702655042.html\" title=\"Generating a DTD from the component's structure overwrites all declarations already stored in the DTD. Fields that are not painted on the component are not added to the DTD.\">Generating a DTD from a Component's Data Structure</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19649e1_d19650e1_d19651e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ihm1665702654967.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ihm1665702654967.html\" title=\"You can use the DTD Wizard to create DTDs based on modeled entities.\">Generating a DTD From a Modeled Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19655e1_d19656e1_d19657e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oed1665702655111.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oed1665702655111.html\" title=\"Use the DTD Editor to define DTDs. Uniface uses DTDs to read and write XML streams.\">Manually Defining DTDs</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19658e1_d19659e1_d19660e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Compile the DTD:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19661e1_d19662e1_d19663e1\">In the DTD Editor, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Compile DTD</span></span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19664e1_d19665e1_d19666e1\">Alternatively, use the command line switch <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dtd</span> to compile your DTDs.\n <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__note_w6611ab1b5b1b7b3b1b3b3_w6612ab1b5b1b7b3b1b3_w6613ab1b5b1b7b3b1_w6614ab1b5b1b7b3_w6615ab1b5b1b7_w6616ab1b5b1_w6617ab1b5_w6618ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If the DTD is not valid, view the Message Frame (Ctrl+M) to locate the problem.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19667e1_d19668e1_d19669e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Make a DTD available to non-Uniface components:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19670e1_d19671e1_d19672e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open the DTD in the DTD Editor and click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Properties</span>.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__li_d19673e1_d19674e1_d19675e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__p_d38858e1_d38859e1_d38860e1\">Enter a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File Name</span>\n                     and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">External Reference</span>.  </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">These properties ensure that the DTD is saved as an external file and that\n                        Uniface references the location in the XML stream generated by the\n                        ProcScript statement <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlsave/ref</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__p_d38861e1_d38862e1_d38863e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlsave/dtd</span> to\n                        include the DTD in the XML stream, ensuring that it is available to 3GL\n                        components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__p_d38864e1_d38865e1_d38866e1\">Uniface components always read DTD data\n                        from a UAR file. 3GL components cannot access the UAR file, so Uniface\n                        provides alternate means to pass DTD information to non-Uniface\n                        components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qkw1665702654897__p_d38867e1_d38868e1_d38869e1\">Only the DTD declarations are made\n                        available. Additional DTD properties, such as the default mapping between\n                        Uniface entities and fields and the DTD, are not provided.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zom1665702566196.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Disconnected Record Sets</a><p>Disconnected record sets provide a way for components to maintain and share data and its state (such as whether the data has been modified) even when a connection to a database is not available. They are typically used for communication between web components (server pages and web services) and are usually implemented as XML, JSON, or Uniface Structs.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohw1665702905473.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Examples of DTDs and XML Streams</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531306\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531306\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Working with DTDs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Working with DTDs Open or create a DTD: In the Uniface IDE, choose More Editors >DTD . Select an existing DTD or enter the name of a new DTD. The Define DTD dialog box is displayed. This is the main interface of the DTD Editor. To open a DTD from a file: In the DTD Editor, choose File >Load from file... and open the desired DTD file. Choose File >Save or compile the DTD to store the DTD in the Repository. To define a DTD, you can generate a DTD from modeled entities or component data structures, or you can manually define a DTD. For more information, see: Generating a DTD from a Component's Data Structure Generating a DTD From a Modeled Entity Manually Defining DTDs Compile the DTD: In the DTD Editor, choose File >Compile DTD . Alternatively, use the command line switch /dtd to compile your DTDs. Note: If the DTD is not valid, view the Message Frame (Ctrl+M) to locate the problem. Make a DTD available to non-Uniface components: Open the DTD in the DTD Editor and click Properties . Enter a File Name and External Reference . These properties ensure that the DTD is saved as an external file and that Uniface references the location in the XML stream generated by the ProcScript statement xmlsave/ref . Use xmlsave/dtd to include the DTD in the XML stream, ensuring that it is available to 3GL components. Uniface components always read DTD data from a UAR file. 3GL components cannot access the UAR file, so Uniface provides alternate means to pass DTD information to non-Uniface components. Only the DTD declarations are made available. Additional DTD properties, such as the default mapping between Uniface entities and fields and the DTD, are not provided. Related Links Disconnected Record Sets Disconnected record sets provide a way for components to maintain and share data and its state (such as whether the data has been modified) even when a connection to a database is not available. They are typically used for communication between web components (server pages and web services) and are usually implemented as XML, JSON, or Uniface Structs. Examples of DTDs and XML Streams Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}